response.overview: If there is one person who knows how to hit the highspots, it's Jack Evans. Also, who better to interview Jack than Rob Naylor, who has been a long time fan and supporter of Jack and his high flying artistry.  Rob travels down memory lane with Jack and discusses his early career in Ring of Honor, including the infamous Teddy Hart incident, as well as Jack's run in Generation Next as Roderick Strong's Chris Tucker to Roddy's Ice Cube.  In a special treat, Angelico sits in with Jack and talks about the current Lucha Libre scene in Mexico and the importance of Lucha Underground to the entire wrestling world.  So sit back and enjoy as Jack Evans is Hitting the Highspots with Rob Naylor.
response.title: Hitting The Highspots - Jack Evans
